All of the spectral simulation model, the photographic pipeline, and the
graphical user interface are the work of Andrea Volpato. This repository
contributes only the changes required to build and run the application as a
self-contained Windows executable. Those changes are described in the project
README under the "Log" section.

This build also bundles third-party open-source dependencies, each retaining
its own license, including (non-exhaustively): PySide6/Qt, napari, vispy,
numba, llvmlite, NumPy, SciPy, colour-science, rawpy, OpenImageIO, Pillow,
dask, and others. Their respective license texts are distributed with their
